{"ast":null,"code":"import{combineReducers,createStore}from'redux';import{authReducer}from'./reducers/authReducer';import{shopReducer}from'./reducers/shopReducer';const rootReducer=combineReducers({auth:authReducer,shop:shopReducer});export const store=createStore(rootReducer);store.subscribe(()=>{const{user}=store.getState().auth;if(user){localStorage.setItem('user',JSON.stringify(user));}else{localStorage.removeItem('user');}});","map":{"version":3,"names":["combineReducers","createStore","authReducer","shopReducer","rootReducer","auth","shop","store","subscribe","user","getState","localStorage","setItem","JSON","stringify","removeItem"],"sources":["C:/Users/merge/OneDrive/Рабочий стол/Sneakershop.narxoz/src/redux/store.js"],"sourcesContent":["import { combineReducers, createStore } from 'redux';\nimport { authReducer } from './reducers/authReducer';\nimport { shopReducer } from './reducers/shopReducer';\n\nconst rootReducer = combineReducers({\n  auth: authReducer,\n  shop: shopReducer\n});\n\nexport const store = createStore(rootReducer);\n\nstore.subscribe(() => {\n  const { user } = store.getState().auth;\n\n  if (user) {\n    localStorage.setItem('user', JSON.stringify(user));\n  } else {\n    localStorage.removeItem('user');\n  }\n});\n"],"mappings":"AAAA,OAASA,eAAe,CAAEC,WAAW,KAAQ,OAAO,CACpD,OAASC,WAAW,KAAQ,wBAAwB,CACpD,OAASC,WAAW,KAAQ,wBAAwB,CAEpD,KAAM,CAAAC,WAAW,CAAGJ,eAAe,CAAC,CAClCK,IAAI,CAAEH,WAAW,CACjBI,IAAI,CAAEH,WACR,CAAC,CAAC,CAEF,MAAO,MAAM,CAAAI,KAAK,CAAGN,WAAW,CAACG,WAAW,CAAC,CAE7CG,KAAK,CAACC,SAAS,CAAC,IAAM,CACpB,KAAM,CAAEC,IAAK,CAAC,CAAGF,KAAK,CAACG,QAAQ,CAAC,CAAC,CAACL,IAAI,CAEtC,GAAII,IAAI,CAAE,CACRE,YAAY,CAACC,OAAO,CAAC,MAAM,CAAEC,IAAI,CAACC,SAAS,CAACL,IAAI,CAAC,CAAC,CACpD,CAAC,IAAM,CACLE,YAAY,CAACI,UAAU,CAAC,MAAM,CAAC,CACjC,CACF,CAAC,CAAC","ignoreList":[]},"metadata":{},"sourceType":"module","externalDependencies":[]}